paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the effects of extracellular acidosis on hERG channels encoded by the KCNH2 gene, focusing on conductance and open time regulation. No specific genetic variants in KCNH2 were reported.

challenges: The paper did not report specific genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on functional studies of the hERG channel and did not provide genetic variant data.
